msgid "chaotic\\_pfc.analysis.sweep"
msgstr ""

#: chaotic_pfc.analysis.sweep:1 of
msgid ""
"Parameter-sweep computation of Lyapunov exponents for the Henon map with "
"an internal FIR filter."
msgstr ""

#: chaotic_pfc.analysis.sweep:4 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"This module sweeps the 2-D grid of filter orders ``N_s in {2, ..., 41}`` "
"against normalised cutoffs ``omega_c in (0, 1)`` and estimates the "
"largest Lyapunov exponent ``lambda_max`` at each grid point."
msgstr ""

#: chaotic_pfc.analysis.sweep:8 of
msgid ""
"All hot paths are JIT-compiled with Numba. The outer 2-D loop is "
"flattened into a single ``prange`` so every grid point is a task "
"available to the thread pool."
msgstr ""

